  "texts": [
    "At the same time, the discriminator evaluates this data against real-world examples, iterating until the generated data is indistinguishable from actual data, at least to the discriminator [9,10].",
    "According to the market research firm Market.us, the global net value of Gen AI in healthcare was approximately $800 million in 2022, with projections to grow to $17.2 billion by 2032 [8].",
    "The healthcare industry has embraced AI-powered solutions, allocating substantial funding to explore their practical benefits.",
    "A recent survey from the Deloitte Center for Health Solutions reveals that approximately 75% of large healthcare organizations are currently using or planning to scale up generative AI in their operations [13].",
    "In 2023, Gen AI technologies made substantial advancements, as evidenced by a recent study in which ChatGPT surpassed physicians in both quality and empathy metrics [14], and Google's MedPaLM-2 LLM achieved expert-level scores on the United States Medical Licensing Examination [15]."
  ],
